{% extends "base.njk" %}
{% from 'banner.njk' import banner as banner %}

{% block content %}
    

    <h1>Welcome to your benefit application</h1>

    {{ banner('blue', '<p>' + __('start.intro.banner') + '</p>') }}

    <p>It usually takes <strong>about 30 minutes to complete</strong> this information online. </p>

    <p>Or call us at <strong>1-888-329-2726 </strong><br>
    Average wait time right now: 20 minutes.</p>


    

    <div><h2>Before you start</h2></div>

    <p>Make sure you have the following details:</p>
    <ul>
    <li>Your SIN number</li>
    <li>Your doctor’s name and contact details</li>

    <li>Information about your diagnosis and treatment</li>
<li>Current medications and dosages.</li>

    </ul>

    <p><h2>Once you’re finished</h2></p>

    <p><strong>2018 average response time: 2 months </strong><br>
from receiving an application to making a decision or asking for more information. </p>

<p><strong>We may need more information</strong> from you. In 2018, about 55% of the applications we received needed some kind of follow-up after the initial submission. </p>

<p>Right now, about 3 million people are receiving this benefit, for a wide range of conditions, including:</p>

<ul>
<li>Depression and/or anxiety</li>
<li>Chronic fatigue syndrome</li>
<li>Cancer</li>

<li>Heart conditions</li>
<li>Injuries and mobility challenges</li>


</ul>

<p>In 2018, we ultimately approved 65% of the applications we received.</p>




    <div>
        <a class="button-link" href="{{ nextRoute }}" role="button" draggable="false">
            {{ __('start.submit') }}
            <span aria-hidden="true">→</span>
        </a>
    </div>

{% endblock %}

{% block scripts %}
    <script type="text/javascript" src={{jsPath}}></script>
{% endblock %}